[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":851},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230924\u002F3283299199\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230924\u002F3283299199\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230924\u002F3283299199\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230924\u002F3283299199\u002F":826,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230924\u002F3283299199\u002F":835},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2023\u002F09\u002F24\u002Fday-10-mongodb-and-mongoose\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":810,"date":811,"description":25,"extension":812,"lang":813,"meta":814,"navigation":191,"path":815,"readingMinutes":816,"seo":817,"standalone":818,"stem":819,"tags":820,"tldr":823,"updated":811,"url":824,"__hash__":825},"content\u002F《Node.js 不負責系列：把前端人員當作後端來用，就算是前端也能嘗試寫的後端～原來 Node.js 可以做這麼多事～》\u002FDay10-MongoDB-與-Mongoose.md","Day10 - MongoDB 與 Mongoose","3283299199",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":798},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,30,33,36,39,42,64,67,93,96,99,105,108,112,115,121,139,142,145,151,154,160,163,166,172,175,228,234,237,243,251,257,264,267,273,276,294,299,305,312,316,319,330,336,339,345,348,352,355,368,371,393,406,422,425,440,443,448,451,454,457,460,467,470,474,477,562,573,631,634,647,650,657,663,666,672,678,683,686,689,692,701,704,752,755,764,772,775,788,791,794],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"MongoDB 與 Mongoose","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fisray_notarray_Mongoose__Mongo_709c6708-2189-4841-bf75-a02c518f682e.png",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"前一篇我們初步對於資料庫有了一點概念後，接下來當然要進入資料庫章節啦～",[20,27,29],{"id":28},"mongodb","MongoDB？",[12,31,32],{},"什麼是 MongoDB 呢？其實 MongoDB 就是我們前一篇文章所介紹的 NoSQL 資料庫，而且前面也有提到 NoSQL 的資料格式類似於 JSON 格式。",[12,34,35],{},"但！！！是！！！！",[12,37,38],{},"MongoDB 其實真正的資料格式是 BSON，而不是 JSON，BSON 是 Binary JSON 的縮寫，是一種二進位的表示形式，因此比 JSON 更加節省空間，而且支援更多的資料型態。",[12,40,41],{},"舉例來講 JSON 格式只有以下",[43,44,45,49,52,55,58,61],"ul",{},[46,47,48],"li",{},"物件（Object）",[46,50,51],{},"陣列（Array）",[46,53,54],{},"字串（String）",[46,56,57],{},"數字（Number）",[46,59,60],{},"布林值（Boolean）",[46,62,63],{},"空值（null）",[12,65,66],{},"而 BSON 則多了以下",[43,68,69,72,75,78,81,84,87,90],{},[46,70,71],{},"日期（Date）",[46,73,74],{},"二進位資料（Binary data）",[46,76,77],{},"正規表示式（Regular expression）",[46,79,80],{},"JavaScript 代碼（JavaScript code）",[46,82,83],{},"ObjectId",[46,85,86],{},"64 位元整數（64-bit integer）",[46,88,89],{},"128 位元浮點數（128-bit floating point number）",[46,91,92],{},"Timestamp",[12,94,95],{},"...等等。",[12,97,98],{},"因此 BSON 又會被稱為是 JSON 的超集合（superset）。",[12,100,101],{},[15,102],{"alt":103,"src":104},"BSON","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002F1694706783597.png",[12,106,107],{},"那麼以上大概就是關於 MongoDB 的重點跟差異，接下來我們就來看看如何使用 MongoDB 吧！",[20,109,111],{"id":110},"mongodb-atlas-註冊","MongoDB Atlas 註冊",[12,113,114],{},"這邊我就不說明本地端的 MongoDB 安裝方式，如果你想要在本地端運作的話，我相信你可以在網路上找到的，取而代之，我會以 MongoDB Atlas 來說明。",[12,116,117],{},[15,118],{"alt":119,"src":120},"叫你去網路上自己 G","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002F1692026406438.png",[122,123,124],"blockquote",{},[12,125,126,130,131,138],{},[127,128,129],"strong",{},"Note","\n如果你真的找不到本地端的安裝方式的話，你可以參考我先前寫的「",[132,133,137],"a",{"href":134,"rel":135},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220213\u002F1357199827\u002F",[136],"nofollow","(1)被迫吃芒果的前端工程師 - 認識 MongoDB 與安裝 MongoDB","」文章；除非有人許願希望我寫一篇本地端安裝的文章，不然我應該不會寫了 XD。",[12,140,141],{},"MongoDB Atlas 是什麼呢？MongoDB Atlas 是由 MongoDB 官方所提供的雲端服務，你可以在上面建立一個 MongoDB 的資料庫，並且透過網路連線的方式來存取資料庫，實戰上來講，我們也比較常見將資料庫放在雲端平台上，當然這不會是絕對，還是會以專案需求為主。",[12,143,144],{},"這邊請你先點擊以下連結進入 MongoDB 的官網，並且註冊一個帳號。",[12,146,147],{},[132,148,149],{"href":149,"rel":150},"https:\u002F\u002Faccount.mongodb.com\u002Faccount\u002Flogin",[136],[12,152,153],{},"這邊我會推薦你使用 GitHub 帳號來註冊",[12,155,156],{},[15,157],{"alt":158,"src":159},"註冊畫面","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fmongodb_login.png",[12,161,162],{},"畢竟身為一名工程師，應該都會有 GitHub 帳號吧？",[12,164,165],{},"基本上你點了註冊後，應該會出現隱私權政策的頁面，你可以直接點選同意，然後就會進入到以下畫面",[12,167,168],{},[15,169],{"alt":170,"src":171},"Welcome","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fmongodb_welcome.png",[12,173,174],{},"這個畫面會稍微需要等一下，接著你應該會跳出它詢問幾個問題，底下我也提供我的選項給你參考",[43,176,177,212,220],{},[46,178,179,180],{},"What is your goal today?\n",[43,181,184,194,200,206],{"className":182},[183],"contains-task-list",[46,185,188,193],{"className":186},[187],"task-list-item",[189,190],"input",{"checked":191,"disabled":191,"type":192},true,"checkbox"," Learn MongoDB",[46,195,197,199],{"className":196},[187],[189,198],{"disabled":191,"type":192}," Explore what I can build",[46,201,203,205],{"className":202},[187],[189,204],{"disabled":191,"type":192}," Migrate an existing application",[46,207,209,211],{"className":208},[187],[189,210],{"disabled":191,"type":192}," Build a new application",[46,213,214,215],{},"What type of application are you building?\n",[43,216,217],{},[46,218,219],{},"I'm just exploring",[46,221,222,223],{},"What is your preferred language?\n",[43,224,225],{},[46,226,227],{},"JavaScript",[12,229,230],{},[15,231],{"alt":232,"src":233},"Welcome2","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fmongodb_alits_welcome.png",[12,235,236],{},"當然你也可以自己選擇，這邊我只是提供一個參考而已，接著你就會進入到以下畫面，也就是選擇你的方案（當然是選 Free 免費方案）",[12,238,239],{},[15,240],{"alt":241,"src":242},"選擇方案","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fmongodb_free.jpg",[12,244,245,246,250],{},"接下來你會進入到 Security Quickstart 畫面，在這邊你可以建立一個可以存取資料庫的使用者，這邊我會建立一個叫做 ",[247,248,249],"code",{},"ithelp"," 的使用者，密碼就讓它隨機產生",[12,252,253],{},[15,254],{"alt":255,"src":256},"Create User","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002FSecurity_Quickstart_MongoDB.jpg",[122,258,259],{},[12,260,261,263],{},[127,262,129],{},"\n這組帳號密碼請務必保存好，因為之後我們會用到它。",[12,265,266],{},"按下建立使用者按鈕後，你應該會跳到「Where would you like to connect from?」區塊，這邊主要是填寫你要從哪裡連線到資料庫，因此我們要選「My Local Environment」",[12,268,269],{},[15,270],{"alt":271,"src":272},"My Local Environment","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002FMy%20Local%20Environment.png",[12,274,275],{},"接下來是「Add entries to your IP Access List」區塊，底下的 IP Address 跟 Description 幫我依照以下填寫並送出",[43,277,278,286],{},[46,279,280,281],{},"IP Address\n",[43,282,283],{},[46,284,285],{},"0.0.0.0",[46,287,288,289],{},"Description\n",[43,290,291],{},[46,292,293],{},"All Ips",[12,295,296],{},[15,297],{"alt":293,"src":298},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002FMongodb_IP_List.jpg",[12,300,301,302,304],{},"這一段 ",[127,303,285],{}," 的意思是「全部的 IP 都可以連線到資料庫」，加入後你就可以按下「Finish and Close」按鈕，這樣你就可以進入到資料庫的畫面了",[122,306,307],{},[12,308,309,311],{},[127,310,129],{},"\n預設 MongoDB 會在你建立資料庫時，自動幫你加入一個你電腦當前 IP 位址；設定為 0.0.0.0 主要是為了方便練習才這樣設定，實戰上並不會這樣做唷。",[20,313,315],{"id":314},"新增-mongodb-atlas-資料庫","新增 MongoDB Atlas 資料庫",[12,317,318],{},"在 Overview 頁面你可以看到有三種方式可以新增資料",[43,320,321,324,327],{},[46,322,323],{},"Add Data",[46,325,326],{},"Load Sample Data",[46,328,329],{},"Data Modeling Templates",[12,331,332],{},[15,333],{"alt":334,"src":335},"Overview","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fmongodb_overview.png",[12,337,338],{},"那麼為了方便示範，我們就選擇「Load Sample Data」，這樣就會幫你篩入一些範例資料，載入過程會需要一點時間，載入完畢後，你應該會看到 Browse Collections 的按鈕，按下去後你就可以看到資料庫的內容了～",[12,340,341],{},[15,342],{"alt":343,"src":344},"Browse Collections","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002FBrowse%20Collections.png",[12,346,347],{},"只要你能看到上面的畫面，那麼我們 MongoDB Atlas 的設定就完成了，接下來我們就可以開始進行連線的設定了～",[20,349,351],{"id":350},"mongoose","Mongoose",[12,353,354],{},"其實官方有提供一個「MongoDB Compass」的工具，這個工具可以幫你連線到 MongoDB Atlas，不過這邊我並不會介紹這個工具，而是會直接使用 Mongoose 來連線到 MongoDB Atlas。",[122,356,357],{},[12,358,359,361,362,367],{},[127,360,129],{},"\n如果你想自己嘗試使用 MongoDB Compass 的話，你可以參考我這一篇文章「",[132,363,366],{"href":364,"rel":365},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220405\u002F475293919\u002F",[136],"(28)被迫吃芒果的前端工程師 - Atlas - MongoDB Compass 教學","」。",[12,369,370],{},"首先這邊請你輸入以下指令來建立新專案",[372,373,378],"pre",{"className":374,"code":375,"language":376,"meta":377,"style":377},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","mkdir example-mongoose\n","bash","",[247,379,380],{"__ignoreMap":377},[381,382,385,389],"span",{"class":383,"line":384},"line",1,[381,386,388],{"class":387},"s_sBn","mkdir",[381,390,392],{"class":391},"sTRMh"," example-mongoose\n",[372,394,396],{"className":374,"code":395,"language":376,"meta":377,"style":377},"cd example-mongoose\n",[247,397,398],{"__ignoreMap":377},[381,399,400,404],{"class":383,"line":384},[381,401,403],{"class":402},"sCcAr","cd",[381,405,392],{"class":391},[372,407,409],{"className":374,"code":408,"language":376,"meta":377,"style":377},"npm init -y\n",[247,410,411],{"__ignoreMap":377},[381,412,413,416,419],{"class":383,"line":384},[381,414,415],{"class":387},"npm",[381,417,418],{"class":391}," init",[381,420,421],{"class":402}," -y\n",[12,423,424],{},"接著請你安裝以下套件",[372,426,428],{"className":374,"code":427,"language":376,"meta":377,"style":377},"npm i mongoose\n",[247,429,430],{"__ignoreMap":377},[381,431,432,434,437],{"class":383,"line":384},[381,433,415],{"class":387},[381,435,436],{"class":391}," i",[381,438,439],{"class":391}," mongoose\n",[12,441,442],{},"安裝完畢後，我們先暫停一下，先讓我們認識一下 Mongoose 是什麼吧！",[444,445,447],"h3",{"id":446},"mongoose-是什麼","Mongoose 是什麼？",[12,449,450],{},"簡單來講 Mongoose 是一個 Node.js 的 ODM（Object Data Modeling），它可以幫助我們在 Node.js 中，更方便的操作 MongoDB 資料庫。",[12,452,453],{},"「難道不能直接使用 MongoDB 操作嗎？」",[12,455,456],{},"答案是可以的，但通常來講我們比較少會直接操作 MongoDB，而是會透過 ODM 來操作，透過 ODM 是可以降低開發與維護的成本，除非你很熟悉 MongoDB，否則會建議你還是使用 ODM。",[12,458,459],{},"那麼什麼是 ODM 呢？ODM 全名是 Object-Document Mapping（物件-文件映射），簡單來講就是將資料庫的文件映射到物件上，這樣就可以透過物件的方式來操作資料庫。",[122,461,462],{},[12,463,464,466],{},[127,465,129],{},"\n另一個則是 ORM - Object-Relational Mapping（物件-關聯映射），這個是用來操作關聯式資料庫的，例如 MySQL、PostgreSQL 等等。",[12,468,469],{},"簡單來講 Mongoose 就是幫你整合了 MongoDB 的操作，讓你可以透過一些它封裝好的方法來操作資料庫，這樣就不用自己寫原生的 MongoDB 指令。",[444,471,473],{"id":472},"連線到-mongodb-atlas","連線到 MongoDB Atlas",[12,475,476],{},"回到剛剛我們建立的專案（example-mongoose），我們先建立一個 index.js 檔案，並輸入以下程式碼",[372,478,482],{"className":479,"code":480,"language":481,"meta":377,"style":377},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","const mongoose = require('mongoose');\n\nmongoose.connect('mongodb+srv:\u002F\u002F\u003C帳號>:\u003C密碼>@cluster0.zyfzacs.mongodb.net\u002F?retryWrites=true&w=majority')\n  .then(() => console.log('Connected to MongoDB...'))\n","js",[247,483,484,510,516,533],{"__ignoreMap":377},[381,485,486,490,493,496,500,504,507],{"class":383,"line":384},[381,487,489],{"class":488},"sWyjQ","const",[381,491,492],{"class":402}," mongoose",[381,494,495],{"class":488}," =",[381,497,499],{"class":498},"sj_SG"," require",[381,501,503],{"class":502},"sMAXC","(",[381,505,506],{"class":391},"'mongoose'",[381,508,509],{"class":502},");\n",[381,511,513],{"class":383,"line":512},2,[381,514,515],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":191},"\n",[381,517,519,522,525,527,530],{"class":383,"line":518},3,[381,520,521],{"class":502},"mongoose.",[381,523,524],{"class":498},"connect",[381,526,503],{"class":502},[381,528,529],{"class":391},"'mongodb+srv:\u002F\u002F\u003C帳號>:\u003C密碼>@cluster0.zyfzacs.mongodb.net\u002F?retryWrites=true&w=majority'",[381,531,532],{"class":502},")\n",[381,534,536,539,542,545,548,551,554,556,559],{"class":383,"line":535},4,[381,537,538],{"class":502},"  .",[381,540,541],{"class":498},"then",[381,543,544],{"class":502},"(() ",[381,546,547],{"class":488},"=>",[381,549,550],{"class":502}," console.",[381,552,553],{"class":498},"log",[381,555,503],{"class":502},[381,557,558],{"class":391},"'Connected to MongoDB...'",[381,560,561],{"class":502},"))\n",[12,563,564,565,568,569,572],{},"要注意沒有 ",[247,566,567],{},"\u003C","、",[247,570,571],{},">"," 符號，因此以範例來講，會長這樣",[372,574,576],{"className":479,"code":575,"language":481,"meta":377,"style":377},"const mongoose = require('mongoose');\n\nmongoose.connect('mongodb+srv:\u002F\u002Fexample:example@cluster0.zyfzacs.mongodb.net\u002F?retryWrites=true&w=majority')\n  .then(() => console.log('Connected to MongoDB...'))\n",[247,577,578,594,598,611],{"__ignoreMap":377},[381,579,580,582,584,586,588,590,592],{"class":383,"line":384},[381,581,489],{"class":488},[381,583,492],{"class":402},[381,585,495],{"class":488},[381,587,499],{"class":498},[381,589,503],{"class":502},[381,591,506],{"class":391},[381,593,509],{"class":502},[381,595,596],{"class":383,"line":512},[381,597,515],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":191},[381,599,600,602,604,606,609],{"class":383,"line":518},[381,601,521],{"class":502},[381,603,524],{"class":498},[381,605,503],{"class":502},[381,607,608],{"class":391},"'mongodb+srv:\u002F\u002Fexample:example@cluster0.zyfzacs.mongodb.net\u002F?retryWrites=true&w=majority'",[381,610,532],{"class":502},[381,612,613,615,617,619,621,623,625,627,629],{"class":383,"line":535},[381,614,538],{"class":502},[381,616,541],{"class":498},[381,618,544],{"class":502},[381,620,547],{"class":488},[381,622,550],{"class":502},[381,624,553],{"class":498},[381,626,503],{"class":502},[381,628,558],{"class":391},[381,630,561],{"class":502},[12,632,633],{},"你只要把你剛剛在 MongoDB Atlas 建立的使用者帳號與密碼填入即可，填入後你就可以執行以下指令來測試連線",[372,635,637],{"className":374,"code":636,"language":376,"meta":377,"style":377},"node index.js\n",[247,638,639],{"__ignoreMap":377},[381,640,641,644],{"class":383,"line":384},[381,642,643],{"class":387},"node",[381,645,646],{"class":391}," index.js\n",[12,648,649],{},"當你有看到「Connected to MongoDB...」這個訊息，那麼恭喜你，你已經成功連線到 MongoDB Atlas 了！",[12,651,652,653,656],{},"ok，這邊其實有一個問題存在，也就是我寫的 ",[247,654,655],{},"mongoose.connect"," 字串並不適用於你，因為每個人都有連線字串，所以這邊該如何取得呢？請你到原本的 MongoDB Atlas 頁面，點選「Connect」",[12,658,659],{},[15,660],{"alt":661,"src":662},"Connect","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fmongodb_atlas_connect.jpg",[12,664,665],{},"然後選擇「Drivers」",[12,667,668],{},[15,669],{"alt":670,"src":671},"Drivers","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fmongodb_atlas_connect_2.jpg",[12,673,674,675,677],{},"接下來你滾到下方你就會看到一個連線字串，請你把它複製下來，並貼到 ",[247,676,655],{}," 中，這樣就可以了～",[12,679,680],{},[15,681],{"alt":661,"src":682},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fmongodb_atlas_connect_3.jpg",[12,684,685],{},"那麼這一段連線字串是怎樣呢？別擔心，這邊我也來拆解說明一下。",[444,687,688],{"id":688},"連線字串",[12,690,691],{},"以我的範例來講，我的連線字串是長這樣",[372,693,695],{"className":479,"code":694,"language":481,"meta":377,"style":377},"'mongodb+srv:\u002F\u002Fexample:\u003Cpassword>@cluster0.zyfzacs.mongodb.net\u002F?retryWrites=true&w=majority'\n",[247,696,697],{"__ignoreMap":377},[381,698,699],{"class":383,"line":384},[381,700,694],{"class":391},[12,702,703],{},"其實這個連線字串是由幾個部分組成的，我們來一個一個拆解",[43,705,706,720,726,732,738],{},[46,707,708,711,712,715,716,719],{},[247,709,710],{},"mongodb+srv:\u002F\u002F","：這是 MongoDB Atlas 的連線字串開頭，",[247,713,714],{},"mongodb+srv"," 表示使用 MongoDB 的 SRV 連線格式，如果你使用的是 MongoDB 的舊版連線格式，那麼這邊就會是 ",[247,717,718],{},"mongodb:\u002F\u002F","。",[46,721,722,725],{},[247,723,724],{},"example","：這是你的使用者帳號，請把它替換成你的使用者帳號。",[46,727,728,731],{},[247,729,730],{},"\u003Cpassword>","：這是你的使用者密碼，請把它替換成你的使用者密碼。",[46,733,734,737],{},[247,735,736],{},"cluster0.zyfzacs.mongodb.net","：這是你的 MongoDB Atlas 位址，請把它替換成你的 MongoDB Atlas 位址。",[46,739,740,743,744,747,748,751],{},[247,741,742],{},"?retryWrites=true&w=majority","：這是 MongoDB Atlas 的參數；",[247,745,746],{},"retryWrites=true"," 意思是說當寫入失敗時，MongoDB Atlas 會自動重試；",[247,749,750],{},"w=majority"," 意思是說當寫入成功時，MongoDB Atlas 會等待大部分的資料庫節點都寫入成功後才回應。",[12,753,754],{},"因此，當你要連線到 MongoDB Atlas 時，你只要把這幾個部分替換成你的資料即可。",[372,756,758],{"className":479,"code":757,"language":481,"meta":377,"style":377},"'mongodb:\u002F\u002F[username:password@]host1[:port1][,...hostN[:portN]][\u002F[defaultauthdb][?options]]'\n",[247,759,760],{"__ignoreMap":377},[381,761,762],{"class":383,"line":384},[381,763,757],{"class":391},[12,765,766,767,719],{},"當然 MongoDB 的連線字串還有很多參數，這邊我就不一一介紹了，如果你想要了解更多，可以參考 ",[132,768,771],{"href":769,"rel":770},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.mongodb.com\u002Fdocs\u002Fmanual\u002Freference\u002Fconnection-string\u002F#connection-string-formats",[136],"MongoDB 官方文件",[12,773,774],{},"啊，這一篇寫得有一點長了，所以這一篇先到這邊結束好了，我們下一篇見囉～",[122,776,777],{},[12,778,779,781,782,787],{},[127,780,129],{},"\n如果你好奇 MongoDB 的基本操作跟語法的話，可以參考我先前寫的「",[132,783,786],{"href":784,"rel":785},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220416\u002F2123631571\u002F",[136],"被迫吃芒果的前端工程師","」，後面章節我可能也不會每個語法都特別介紹，所以建議如果你不熟悉的話，可以考慮先閱讀一下。",[20,789,790],{"id":790},"碎碎念",[12,792,793],{},"去年其實就一直想說要寫 Node.js，結果今年要寫的時候就遇上公司的 Node.js 課程開班，結果一路忙到快開賽才準備要寫的內容，然後寫著寫著...怎麼那麼多 RRRRRRR",[795,796,797],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .sj_SG, html code.shiki .sj_SG{--shiki-default:#DBB7FF